      "speakers": [],
      "text": "郭得福下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00023",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "郭得福上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00024",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "今日下山无得财，获住乡民女裙衩。吩咐喽兵松了绑，将民女与我带上来！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00025",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "姜美容上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00026",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "与大王叩头。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00027",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "你这一女子，家住哪里，姓甚名谁？对本大王一讲。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00028",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "大王容禀！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00029",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "战兢兢跪在了山坡以上，叫一声大王爷细听分明：",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00030",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "家住哪里？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00031",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "家住在山西太原府，随波门来到永平城。郭老爷在京把尚书做，我是他儿妻姜氏美容。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00032",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "说起别人我不晓，提起郭家我知情。郭老爷他有几个子？几个亲生几螟蛉？",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00033",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "郭老爷他有四个子，两个亲生二螟蛉。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00034",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "二亲生来二螟蛉，你与哪个配婚成？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00035",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "我夫名叫郭得福，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00036",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "他为官来他为民？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00037",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "儿父名叫一总镇，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00038",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "看起来他是官门中。吩咐令人打上座，来路之事问过清。说了实话还罢了，一字说错活不成。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00039",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "八月中秋赴寿诞，张意挂画在庭前。张意挂画挂不正，恼怒我父二品官。我父打他四十棍，张意贼怀恨在心前。灯下写了无头卷，四门四张五门悬。又叫仇官揩了去，奏与唐皇主圣贤。唐王爷听信奸臣话，带领人马抄家眷。三百余口俱杀死，",
      "text_length": 106
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00040",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "他不杀你为哪般？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00041",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "小奴本是宦门女，岂能配他下贱残？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00042",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "既然不愿成亲事，何人把你容颜扳？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00043",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "话到舌边我难讲，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00044",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "半言半语为哪般？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00045",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "奴家身怀有了孕，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00046",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "我问你分娩不分娩？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00047",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "奴家生下郭门后，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00048",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "怎么不见你儿男？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00049",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "张意贼记心间，要害郭门后根源。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00050",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "张意要害你儿命，何人救他一命还？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00051",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "多亏他家老张保，施了亲生救螟蛉。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00052",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "施亲生来救螟蛉，他岂肯与你罢不成？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00053",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "万般出在无计奈，火炎草堂归阴城。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00054",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "出永平来离永平，黑夜女郎哪里行？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00055",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "今日一到太原府，太原府里去搬兵。太原府搬的人马到，好与郭门报冤恨。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00056",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "我当你是哪个到，原是我妻姜美容。意思不把她来认，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00057",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "咳呀，罢了！夫人哪！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00058",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "走上前来把妻认，再把夫人叫一声。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00059",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "听一言来好心惊，骂声恶贼细耳听：拿刀来把我头割下，想要成亲万不能！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00060",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "我妻不必胆战惊，丈夫把话对你明：把我当作哪一个？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00061",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "你是哪个？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00062",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "我是你丈夫郭得福。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00063",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "儿夫三绺胡须下，你像三国二关公。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00064",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "郭得福"
      ],
      "text": "好叫夫人得知晓，听我把话对你明：也是我高山闭了脸，因此落得像关公。喽啰看过净面水，净面水里洗面容。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01018008_e00065",
      "play_id": "01018008",
      "scene_id": "01018008_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姜美容"
      ],
      "text": "果然你是我丈夫到，拿着何物作证明？若有金钗和玉带，快快拿来对相逢。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
